title: The Latest: Carson says no Democrat would be tough to beat
text: > Texas The Latest: Carson says no Democrat would be tough to beat FILE - in this Oct. 12, 2015 file photo, Republican presidential candidate, Sen. Ted Cruz, R-Texas, speaks in Rockwell City, Iowa. White House spokesman Josh Earnest mixed his politics and sports to jab at Republican presidential candidate Ted Cruz. Earnest jokingly described Toronto as Cruz’s other hometown team, a reference to the Texas senator being born in Canada. Earnest says he’s open to a bet between the two. (AP Photo/Charlie Neibergall, File)
